Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I took him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I took out the shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.94,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}C-Calm down, Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.18,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's just unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:39.20,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We need to get him help, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.85,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Found Whitey and Blondie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:46.89,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be faster to cut him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Your way of moving faster is too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.29,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Shogun-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.70,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The former shogun, \NSadasada-sama is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.05,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you available?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he available?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I want to know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a disaster! What the hell \Ndo we do about this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We finally found the former shogun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.14,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the current shogun is flying away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Butterflying away in the River Styx.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, we'll be \Nbutterflying away with him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.31,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so before that, let's start running away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.78,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.27,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.11,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna give up \Non this perfect chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.26,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.41,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeshige-san is my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.74,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need his permission to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.50,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in, Shigeshige-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.92,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.62,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.17,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We said to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.43,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Shogun-sama is busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.75,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, we're Delivery \NYoshiwara's Nobume...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.94,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,...and Tsu-ki. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:59.95,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the Palace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.95,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Found the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.45,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Shot Grampy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.75,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I already found everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.53,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for being an elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.11,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Sasaki-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:13.92,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,We were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.66,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.63,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,But watch where you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.46,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I almost mistook you for \Na villain and shot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.41,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Almost? You nearly shot me to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.58,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten-dono, if you agree \Nto take responsibility when
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.23,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally kill the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.15,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,we can play another round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.55,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop! We're going to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.02,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.18,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.13,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I would expect as much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.03,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from Rotten Maizo-dono, \Nadvisor to the former shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:48.04,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you gave up your \Nleft arm to show your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.24,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy, you served Sadasada-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.04,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:59.75,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It was a tempestuous age of \Npolitical purges within the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:04.80,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,and Rotten-dono played a pivotal \Nrole in keeping his master safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.30,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sadasada-sama's elevation to shogun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,was thanks to Rotten-dono's hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:15.98,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,since the other candidates \Nwere all sent to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.98,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by "heaven," I mean Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.17,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.99,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-dono, could you escort \Nthese visitors outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.86,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.04,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Grampy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.06,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.43,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Soyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.68,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Shogun-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.23,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Shogun-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.37,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're spilling everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.66,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not a chance in hell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way we can fool him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are we bothering with this act?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His eyes are rolled back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The former shogun's eyes \Nare also rolled back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.18,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Say something! Say something, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a ventriloquist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.23,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Still beats staying quiet! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you gave me a scare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,since you walked in without \Nany warning, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I look like a fool now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.35,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so casual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.31,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Act more serious, like the shogun would!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Genda Tessho-san here, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to \Nplay a serious shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.93,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Dearest Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She can mimic voices?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.47,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I have humiliated myself shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh, shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.59,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:33.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Why do you end every \Nsentence with shogun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.50,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what you saw shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're sounding like Korosuke now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you trying to imitate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.13,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.54,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The shogun is talking faster than \Nhis mouth can move shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody asked for an \NIkkoku-dou impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be the one apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.54,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to frown upon such behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:59.25,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I did some crazy things when I was young, \Nthough nothing as bold as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does he think was going on here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:05.69,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm shocked that the Mimawarigumi \Nwould allow visitors inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.19,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they aren't \Nhere to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.05,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er, can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can I just stare at his \Nreceding hairline from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.06,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.31,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Get over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.31,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They claim to be training, but \Nthat's no more than an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.82,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They're monitoring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.17,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You know that the current Bakufu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.00,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.68,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,is split between our faction, \Nwhich backs you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.69,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,and the faction that \Nwants to make one of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.24,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the young Hitotsubashis Shogun, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.79,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The recent assassination victims
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.34,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,have all been members of \Nthe Hitotsubashi faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,That is why they suspect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:47.36,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The Mimawarigumi have strong ties \Nto the Hitotsubashi faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.26,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They may attempt to make \Nfalse accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:56.64,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to do anything that would \Nattract their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.73,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Shogun-sama, give me back my underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.81,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Any naughty underwear around shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, this stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:08.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeshige-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.22,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Was your hair always so bushy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this hair was on her underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:18.12,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that bushy object \Nbeing in this room before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.87,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this hair was always here shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.59,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I can't tell if you're \Nbeing resilient or foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, it worked?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.20,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,But try to control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:36.64,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen many people ruin \Ntheir lives because of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.71,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, beware of courtesans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.75,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.19,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.57,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,But there is something I must ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:52.91,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the courtesan Suzuran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.27,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't matter if \Nyou don't remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.41,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I just... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.91,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.70,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to know the \Nconnection between
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.42,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that courtesan and Sadasada-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like you knew something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.09,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Let me offer you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.13,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your e-mail \Naddresses and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.58,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.46,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Become my e-mail buddies and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.10,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,We'd rather stay strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.93,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,The courtesan who bewitched \Nand toppled our very country...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.82,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, unless you \Nwant to get yourself destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.97,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.36,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,So Suzuran is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.87,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:41.62,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Suzuran was Sadasada-sama's \Ncompanion when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.34,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,However, he wasn't the one \Nwho fell for her charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.73,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, Yoshiwara was a place for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.41,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,high-ranking officials \Nto meet and socialize,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:56.58,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,and every man who visited \Nwas entranced by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.80,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.39,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.08,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I could never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes shining with kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.13,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The graceful way she moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.40,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Her silky hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.40,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Glossy lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Supple skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.74,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:27.19,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,...those blood-stained hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:33.05,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to suck them off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.55,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,He was using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:41.06,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Using her as a tool to \Ntopple this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.68,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,And after becoming shogun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.35,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,he prepared a puppet to succeed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.57,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,so his influence in the \Npalace would not wane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.86,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,What about that promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.05,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,would grant freedom to a tool \Nwho knew his secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.37,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,If he ever made such a \Npromise, he was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.37,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing more than a \Ncurse to maintain control
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.41,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,over his tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.17,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That cunning old man is not \Nsomeone you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.79,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home and let \Nthe elites deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.09,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiwara was only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.38,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,This place has become \Nhis hunting ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.62,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what might happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.68,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a curry udon \Nstain out the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:32.61,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you that you \Nwere asking for trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.57,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-Sasaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.86,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've found some more tools to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.83,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:47.37,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,These criminals are guilty of \Nmurdering Bakufu officials
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.87,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the leader \Nof those snooping dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.92,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki was taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:11:01.18,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his life was forfeit once he \Nlet murderers inside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.56,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,The Mimawarigumi have been \Nremoved from palace security.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.56,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before they disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:11.69,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,And we've been selected \Nto take their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.15,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,But something about this stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.57,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Stinks?! What does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:18.09,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the alleged criminals in the serial \NBakufu murders were apprehended,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.08,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll be executed \Ntomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,without conducting any investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.86,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like they're trying \Nto cover something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.02,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, whew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.77,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought he could smell my gas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.58,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.05,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.83,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.99,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's clean up these murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kondo-kun! Hijikata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy meeting you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you, you rotten cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't ignore me! Hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.27,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless. That's some stubborn \Nfilth they're covered in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.52,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,That won't ever clean off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! That gorilla pooped a \Nlittle when he farted earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.94,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.70,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.45,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the wrong enemy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.95,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's going to lend \Nan ear to your pleas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.46,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Then rip off your ear \Nand lend it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.97,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my ears have a prior engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:17.00,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then give me an ear of corn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.00,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I see a familiar face in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:21.51,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. Why is there an \Nelite locked up with the scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.00,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the Mimawarigumi \Nif I tell the shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.33,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:30.89,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you guys are \Nalready finished, regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.10,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over a Pon De Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.40,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you want?! \NYou're ripping me apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.76,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.20,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We really picked the wrong \Nopponent this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:49.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san said that the palace was \NSadasada's hunting ground now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.25,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And Sasaki-san was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.16,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.75,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Isaburo is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.48,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,So it turns out you were right, Gintoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.79,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one blinded by a false dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.76,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran was waiting for a \Nman that doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.37,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,She must have known
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.80,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,that refusing Sadasada \Nwould mean her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:18.52,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,That the promise was meant \Nto chain her to Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.53,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran wasn't waiting for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.53,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,She had no choice but \Nto cling to her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.79,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeshige-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.29,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.41,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are Princess \NSoyo's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.67,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,If you must punish someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:44.67,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,please slice off my ass instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.45,Main01,Shogun,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Grampy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.84,Main01,Shogun,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle was the one \Nwho saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.55,Main01,Shogun,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:54.54,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the only \None who can stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.30,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.56,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They are murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:04.69,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you saying that I'm lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.16,Main01,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,B-By no means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.58,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest, Shigeshige-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:17.61,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,This old man will take care \Nof everything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.00,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Sadasada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.37,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.63,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's true, \Nbut that's their story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.13,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.94,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.31,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to defend Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.14,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our problem if those pigs \Nwant to feed on one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.87,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,But if we ignore what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.77,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be no better than them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.63,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that those \Npigs are the only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.53,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,we country boys get to play samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:50.28,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in being a bogus \Nsamurai that doesn't follow a code!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:53.81,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,We have to play bogus samurai \Nif we want to defend anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.79,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize that this is what \Nwe're supposed to be defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.52,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.29,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get any sleep, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.04,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Soyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she going to save us while \Nthose fools are fighting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:18.34,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I was having trouble \Nfalling asleep all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.65,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.88,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gotten used to Nobume-san \Nsleeping with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was too scared to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.57,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we're the ones who should \Nbe too scared to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.28,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little nervous since this \Nis almost like a sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we're the ones who \Nshould be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.29,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be executed tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.17,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:40.82,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy will prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.79,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you still can't fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.29,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.12,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you some bedtime stories
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:49.05,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that Grampy told me when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.05,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,They're so boring that you'll \Nfall asleep in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.05,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.05,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How boring do you expect it to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.56,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:04.12,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, there was \Na lord and his retainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:08.03,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,The lord's wife was the most \Nbeautiful princess in the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.57,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,and she cared about him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:14.84,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,But the lord used the \Nprincess's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:18.74,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,threw her in prison, and forced\N her to do terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.83,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,The princess could only cry \Nin her prison every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:29.76,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,The retainer felt sorry for the princess \Nand often came to wipe her tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:36.06,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for he had fallen in \Nlove with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.36,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.52,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dispose of Suzuran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.10,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,The retainer would be \Nkilled if he didn't obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.46,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't bring himself \Nto kill the woman he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.72,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, they made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.21,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,They would escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.78,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I will take you with me on the \Nnight of the next full moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:02.29,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,And then they exchanged a pinky swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.79,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,But he never returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.71,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,for the lord already knew about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.66,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long will Suzuran wait for you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.18,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a man who's long forgotten his promise?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.52,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The woman will wait for \Nthe rest of her life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.97,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for a man who will never come,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.85,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while the man will live \Nthe rest of his life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the pain of breaking his promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.71,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A beautiful story, yes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.47,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,If the retainer were to go see the \Nprincess, she would be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:37.15,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Their promise was transformed \Ninto a chain heavier than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.32,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,So he swore to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.65,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter how many \Nfull moons came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.07,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter if they \Nwere covered in wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:49.26,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter if the \Nprincess forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.71,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,He would live until the day he met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:58.34,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,And so, he continues to live by \Ncrawling on his three limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:01.32,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Maizo, I heard something \Nfascinating that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.22,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to pass on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.23,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran is still living in Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.23,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,But she won't survive much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.73,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.06,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,How many full moons have come and gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.04,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's time to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.40,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:24.24,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Take responsibility for inviting \Nthose criminals into the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.80,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Disembowel yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.75,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran will be waiting \Nfor you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.10,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,And the princess and retainer were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.81,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.26,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard enough, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.44,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't able to fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We already know the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.31,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you open the door \Nnow, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.83,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.69,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.98,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,They were tossed in when you entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.90,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.41,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Come out here. It's time \Nfor your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.04,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Put on your execution clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.22,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, don't forget you \Nhave an appointment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with the executioner's block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:15.07,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come back \Nwith your head attached
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.67,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,since we'll need to chop it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.45,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Try to commit a crime that's \Nworthy of this punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.76,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,What crime will you be guilty of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The crime of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,ripping off a lord's \Ntopknot down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:33.02,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,This may be the last \Ntime we send him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.02,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.53,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've sided with \Nus, there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.59,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:45.16,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause an uproar, that old man \Nwill start to show his true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:50.54,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Once there's no one left to \Ninterfere, we'll grill him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.04,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,So you can go die in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.55,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want me to dispatch you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.06,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.85,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.93,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,You have no allies in this palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.94,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't prepared to take over \Nthis country, you'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.45,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.07,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be eliminated by \Nthat old man instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.82,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to join in the \Nbattle for this nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.75,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,forget about anything \Nbeing black or white.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:29.70,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.60,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Are there more bandits about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:45.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Zura would love to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought we'd be trying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:50.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to seize this country for \Nthe sake of an old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This makes us wanted criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis won't be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.91,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, sister lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.36,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no place for us \Non Earth, we'll go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.37,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The independent city Yoshiwara \Nwill keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs in Yoshiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:15.00,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's a gay bar \Nthat's understaffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.50,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll be seizing your \Nballs after you seize this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.07,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.95,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hit me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who \Nbrought her with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who taught \Nher those dirty jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:30.12,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for telling dirty \Njokes to innocent little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.57,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Girls our age absorb \Neverything like sponges!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A sponge?! You're more like a \Ndirty rag soaked in milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.73,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, toilet paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I at least deserve to be called a rag! \NA rag used to wipe asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.24,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.77,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be sacrificing \Neverything for Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I already made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.92,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.99,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:02.92,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:05.92,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We will all return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.98,Tsuzuku,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:47.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:49.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There was the One Piece film \Nat the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:52.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then you've got Hunter x Hunter and \NDragon Ball films in spring, and us in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:57.51,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,We should ask TV Tokyo to show our \Nmovie with the Pokemon movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:23:58.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:23:59.43,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:04.88,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Five Fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:10.05,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The Bakufu army stands in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:10.05,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Overwhelming manpower!! Firepower!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:14.91,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,to seize this country!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:14.91,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Our five heroes have made a promise
